title: Slade - Slayed? (1972) (2006 Japan) FLAC
description:
Slade - Slayed? (1972) [Japan Mini-LP CD 2006]

2006 Japanese issue limited edition 24-Bit digitally remastered 13-track CD album, originally released in 1972, a classic album from Noddy & the boys, including 'Gudbuy T' Jane' and 'Mama Weer All Crazee Now' plus 3 bonus track.

Tracklist:

1. How D'You Ride (3:11)
2. The Whole World's Goin' Crazee (3:36)
3. Look At Last Nite (3:05)
4. I Won't Let It 'Appen Agen (3:16)
5. Move Over (3:44)
6. Gudbuy T'Jane (3:32)
7. Gudbuy Gudbuy (3:29)
8. Mama Weer All Crazee Now (3:43)
9. I Don' Mind (3:06)
10. Let The Good Times Roll / Feel So Fine (3:55)
11. Take Me Bak 'Ome (Bonus track for Japan) (3:16)
12. Cum On Feel The Noize (Bonus track for Japan) (4:25)
13. Skweeze Me, Pleeze Me (Bonus track for Japan) (4:32)

Produced by Chas Chandler
Remastered by Yoshiro Kuzumaki

Band
Noddy Holder - lead vocals, rhythm guitar
Dave Hill - lead guitar
Jim Lea - bass guitar, piano
Don Powell - drums
